<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa kha hngak ko, Bia a kan kam bangin, Bawipa kha hngak ko, Van in
 a tum lai, Bawipa kha hngak ko, Zumhnak in hngak ko, Na lungthin dihlak
 in hngak ko.

[C1]
   Hi thawnnak, Hi thawnnak, Thiannak le sualnak, tei khotu thawnnak a
   si, Hi thawnnak, Hithawn nak, Pen-te-cos ni hmuhmi thawnnak.

[V2]
