 thlah kan si cang, Bawipa kha hngak ko, Van thli hmuh awkah, Na lungthin
 dihlak in hngak ko.

[C2]
   Hi thawnnak, Hi thawnnak, Thiannak le sualnak, tei khotu thawnnak a
   si, Hi thawnnak, Hithawn nak, Pen-te-cos ni hmuhmi thawnnak.

[V3]
 Bawipa kha hngak ko, Tlangsang deuh kha cuan law, Bawipa kha hngak ko,
 Ruahnak sangpi he, Bawipa kha hngak ko, Van mei hmuh awkah, Na lungthin
 dihlak in hngak ko.

[C3]
   Hi thawnnak, Hi thawnnak, Thiannak le sualnak, tei khotu thawnnak a
   si, Hi thawnnak, Hithawn nak, Pen-te-cos ni hmuhmi thawnnak.</lyrics>
